==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From a compound of  [[διά]] {{GG|1223}} and  [[δέω ]] {{GG|1210}}; 

===Pronunciation===
διάδημα / diadēma  / dee-ad'-ay-mah

===Noun===
'''διάδημα'''

# a “[[diadem]]” (as bound about the head): - [[crown]]. 

